726728f-b.title: Queens: Fresh Pond Road - Catalpa Avenue
726728f-b.text:
Fresh Pood Road (tracks thereon), at the S.W. corner of Catalpa
Ave., showing the John C. De Bevoise house from 1852 to 1873. This
house which has been added to is now occupied by the Ridgewood Court
(E. of C.) and the Fifth District City Magistrates Court, which
opened here on March 15, 1922. In View No. 1, Public School No. 88
is partially seen at the extreme right.
1922.
Views 1 and 3.
View 2: March 1923.
Eugene L, Armbruster Collection.
